descriptionHtml:
Turknstarr is a collapsing Dwemer Ruin in between The Tower Stone and Pilgrim's Trench. The ruin is leveled and I highly recommend you be at least level 40+ when venturing into the ruins. If you possess godlike attributes, then this mod will present no difficulty to you whatsoever as you will dismantle every single thing in your path. There is no quest within this mod as I feel that this dungeon doesn't need a story to it.

This is my very first attempt at making a mod for Skyrim, so there might be quite a lot of bugs. If there are any present, I would love to hear about it as I absolutely welcome criticism of all sorts. That is the only way I could improve really.

There is no DLC requirement and no conflicts with any mods that I know of.
author: RavenousBookcase
